Package: SmoothOperator
Title: Easy Feature Engineering with mgcv Penalized Spline Smooths
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Hannes", "Riebl", email = "hriebl@uni-goettingen.de",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A convenient API for working with penalized spline smooths,
    based on the mgcv package. The smooths can easily be integrated with
    user-defined models and algorithms.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: mgcv (>= 1.8-36), R6 (>= 2.5.0)
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
